author: danielsh
msg: Refactor FSFS locks walker to separate walking the digest files
from walking the locks.  There should be no functional change.
This involved moving some functionality from walk_digest_files()
into a wrapper walker API, walk_locks().
New walker API, has the functionality walk_digest_files() had up to this commit.
